headline: CIBC Asset Management announces revised CIBC ETF cash distributions for December 2025
summary: CIBC (TSX: CM) (NYSE: CM) – CIBC Asset Management Inc. today announced the revised December 2025 cash distributions for CIBC ETFs and ETF Series of the CIBC Fixed Income Pools and CIBC Sustainable Investment Solutions.
